      "factorStatus": "not-assessed",
      "acceptanceCriteria": "Demonstration that input parameters used in validation simulations are equivalent to those in the COU simulations, or documented justification for any differences.",
      "rationale": "Boundary conditions in validation simulations (inlet velocity profiles, outlet pressure) were set to match bench test conditions rather than COU operating conditions. No equivalency analysis bridging validation inputs to COU inputs has been documented. Achieved level 1 below required level 3; epistemic gap."
